section.def:
appellant
                (上訴人) means a person who serves a notice of
            appeal under section 3;

Authority
                (主管當局) means the Director of Food and
            Environmental Hygiene;

Chairman
                (主席) has the meaning specified in section
                128A(2) of the Ordinance;

secretary
                (秘書) means the person appointed as secretary to
            the Appeal Board under section 128D(6)(a) of the Ordinance;
